data.description: Perched high in the Ozark mountains on 5 acres, this must-see custom-built ranch showcases incredible views that are guaranteed to impress. Gorgeous hardwood floors and tall ceilings flow throughout including in the living room where a vaulted beamed ceiling and a cozy wood-burning fireplace await. Custom cabinetry, a wood sink, quality stainless steel appliances and sweeping granite countertops will delight any passionate cook. The bedrooms are large and there are 2 full baths including the master bath with a freestanding tub. There is an office or a potential 3rd bedroom housed in the detached 2-car garage. The long list of additional features includes wood panel walls, ceiling fans and a laundry/mudroom. You can take your pick from a range of outdoor spaces where you can entertain guests, cook on the grill and admire the awe-inspiring sunrise and sunset views. This incredible home is serviced by quality Plato schools and is just moments from Beaver Creek and 1.5hrs from Springfield.
